Author: Zi Yan <ziy@nvidia.com>

selftests/mm: add folio_split() and filemap_get_entry() race test

This commit adds a C port of a race condition test between folio_split()
and filemap_get_entry(). It creates shmem huge pages and punches holes in
them while 16 threads continuously read the memory.

